WEBVTT

00:00.340 --> 00:02.160
So, you wanna be a fighter?

00:04.330 --> 00:05.700
It's not just how hard you hit...

00:07.800 --> 00:09.410
...or how fast you can move,...

00:11.440 --> 00:13.610
...or how many strikes you can absorb without tapping out.

00:15.680 --> 00:17.780
It's about getting up earlier, training harder...

00:19.820 --> 00:21.780
...and pushing yourself more than the other guys.

00:23.920 --> 00:25.960
It's about knowing you could be the best...

00:28.220 --> 00:30.390
...and doing everything in your power to make it a reality.

00:32.700 --> 00:34.400
It's about courage and commitment.

00:36.270 --> 00:37.230
That's what it takes.

00:39.339 --> 00:40.940
So, you wanna be a fighter?

00:45.080 --> 00:45.870
This is how.

